fa107805-2b38-4683-baea-465e2a19502e.text: “Halo” by Beyoncé is an emotional pop ballad about love and redemption that creates an uplifting mood through Beyoncé's powerful voice.

73826a63-dafe-49bb-8a75-3cf1cd8b968c.text: “Eastside” by Benny Blanco, Halsey & Khalid is a nostalgic pop song about the joy of remembering, with a simple but infectious rhythm that creates a positive and uplifting atmosphere.

0df018ee-09b7-4d1a-9383-7da3841f359e.text: “Bad Guy” by Billie Eilish is a minimalist electro-pop song with an ironic attitude that stands out for its unconventional style and dark humor.

2fe4f901-66e4-42f7-8f06-0c0749627099.text: “Smells Like Teen Spirit” by Nirvana is a rebellious grunge classic about youthful frustration, whose raw energy and distorted guitar riffs characterized the 90s.
